          "name": "Explore Data",
          "icon": "data-files",
          "body": "The Explorer page gives you insights and a clear overview of data.",
          "link": "/explorer",
          "label": "Explore data"
        },
        {
          "name": "Access Data",
          "icon": "data-access",
          "body": "Getting metadata and other clinical variables exposed by API in our secure cloud environment.",
